headline: Mettler-Toledo International Q4 Earnings Call Highlights
summary: Mettler-Toledo International (NYSE:MTD) executives said the company closed 2025 with “broad-based growth” in the fourth quarter, despite a challenging environment that included trade disputes, soft end markets, and tariff impacts. Management highlighted execution on its Spinnaker sales and marketing
